<p>书画家代表现场创作中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20191029/f8ca072a9ae54ae3a47c3ec0596177ac.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
